text: Alexia Magalhães (born 13 September 2000) is a Luxembourger footballer who plays as a midfielder for Dames Ligue 1 club FCM Young Boys Diekirch and the Luxembourg women's national team. ==International career== Magalhães made her senior debut for Luxembourg on 21 June 2019 during a 2–1 friendly win against Andorra. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Luxembourgian women's footballers Category:Luxembourg women's international footballers Category:Luxembourgian people of Portuguese descent
